{"questionId":"22529033","questionHtml":"<p>Write down an expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math> in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>let <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>R</mi></msub></math> denote the area of the rectangle and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi></msub></math> denote the area of the semicircle<br>one correct area <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>R</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mi>h</mi></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>S</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22529033","referenceCode":"24M.2.SL.TZ2.8a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Write down an expression for A in terms of x and h.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","Prior learning","Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","SL 3.4—Circle: radians, arcs, sectors"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}